column5: I completely get how u feel. Sometimes I feel like I give so much to people and they don't even try to recognize that um hello I am a human being too.

No one knows the real me and it's honestly devastating I want to do and say things and be myself and I cant idk how because all my life I have always known that I must act accordingly and now I can even remember being my true self or what it was even like....I feel truly alone
Happens to me almost all the time and idk how to stop
